<title>lsạny lyk bysbḥ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- lsạny lyk bysbḥ dạ ạ̉nt gẖạly ʿly
 sẖkr wḥmd yqdm lyk yạ yswʿ fạdy
 ạlqrạr - bkl kyạny yạ rb ạ̉nạ lyk wttẖbt ʿyny dạymạaⁿ ʿlyk
 hyfḍl qlby mạsk fyk ḥty fy wqt ạlḍyq
 2- wdạny tsmʿ klạmk wdạymạaⁿ tʿml byh
 wṣạyạk ʿlṭwl qdạmy wṣwtk mstnyh
 3- ʿyny tqrạ fy ktạbk ạnk sẖkẖṣ ʿẓym
 wạtʿlm mn ṣfạtk rb mḥb rḥym</lyrics>
</song>